high_descs: Go to the green trash bin
Pick up a roll from the bin
Turn around and move across the room to face the black table
Put the roll on the table
Turn around, go to the toilet and face the toilet paper roll
Pick up the toilet paper roll from the handle
Go back to the table
Place the paper roll on the table
anns.task_desc: Place an empty roll and a paper roll on the table

high_descs: Turn right and step forward to face the back of the toilet.
Pick up the empty roll on the back of the toilet.
Turn around and step forward to face the black table.
Place the empty roll on the black table.
Turn right and step forward to face the toilet paper on the wall.
Remove the toilet paper from the holder on the wall.
Turn right to face the black table.
Place the toilet paper on the black table.
anns.task_desc: To move a roll of toilet paper plus an empty roll to the black table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the green bin on the floor to the left.
Pick up the empty roll of toilet paper from the left side of the toilet tank.
Turn around and walk to the small black table.
Put the empty roll of toilet paper in the middle of the black table.
Turn around and walk to the wall in front of the white toilet on the right.
Pick up the full roll of toilet paper from the black metal holder on the wall.
Turn around and walk to the small black table on the left.
Put the full roll of toilet paper to the left of the empty roll on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place two rolls of toilet paper on a table.
